    "difficulty": "Hard",
    "passage": "The fossil remains of the individual known as Oase 1, discovered in Romania in 2002, can help paleoanthropologists not only ______ steps in the evolution of hominids but also illuminate the Pleistocene epoch generally, revealing important details about the time in which Oase 1 lived.",
