    "skill": "Transitions",
    "difficulty": "Hard",
    "passage": "Modernista architects championed nature in their designs. ______ the wavy staircase and ornate floral tilework of Hospital de Sant Pau, a Modernista hospital designed by Lluís Domènech i Montaner, couldn’t exactly grow in a forest. Still, one sees natural influences in Domènech i Montaner’s penchant for curves (rather than right angles) and plant- and animal-inspired flourishes.",
