    "skill": "Words in Context",
    "difficulty": "Hard",
    "passage": "Despite how ______ they may seem on first glance, the works of the philosopher Georg Hegel have proven to be quite influential. Readers who manage to penetrate Hegel’s frustratingly dense prose often find that his thrillingly original and profound ideas wind up shaping their own thinking.",
